name: Peep Show - A Series of Peculiar Portraits

metadata.name: 'JOSEPHINE'
metadata.description:
This work originates from a series called 'Peep Show - A Series of Peculiar Portraits.'

They aim to be surreal explorations of culture and traditional dress. With a radical attempt to depart from the political they aim to submerge the viewer into a more ethereal and whimsical space. Their aesthetic bound in artifice and the theatrical.
